content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 319.311 - Chow mein vegetables with meat and chop suey vegetables with meat

State Regulations
"Chow Mein Vegetables with Meat" and "Chop Suey

Vegetables with Meat" shall contain not less than 12 percent meat computed on
the weight of the uncooked fresh meat prior to its inclusion with the other
ingredients. Notes
